        "description": "META QUEST 3 VISUAL UPDATE OUT NOW!\n\nIn this story-driven adventure, you play an intergalactic agent with unique Mentalic powers that allow you to read minds, influence emotions, and destroy your enemies.\n\nYour mission is of utmost importance: it will determine the future of humanity.\n\nDisguise, hack, and blast your way through Isaac Asimov's groundbreaking sci-fi universe using the most advanced tools the Galactic Empire has to offer.\n\nWill you stay loyal to a crumbling Empire, or forge a new future in the Foundation?\n\nFaithfully adapted from Asimov's groundbreaking groundbreaking novels, Journey to Foundation is a gripping narrative adventure unlike anything else you can find in VR.\n\n·   Befriend or double-cross the people around you, and choose who lives or dies\n\n·   Participate in the drama through conversation, time-sensitive gestures, and a story that reacts to your choices\n\n·   Interact with over 90 fully-voiced characters brought to life by a top-tier voice cast including Jennifer Hale, François Chau, and Jason Hightower\n\n·   Available with full voice acting and text in English, French, German, and Spanish\n\n·   Accessibility options that keep you comfortable and let you play your way",
